Package org.biojava.nbio.core.sequence

Class AccessionID

java.lang.Object
org.biojava.nbio.core.sequence.AccessionID
public class AccessionID extends Object
Used in Sequences as the unique identifier. If possible, set the DataSource to know the source of the id. This allows a SequenceProxy to gather features or related sequences Protein->Gene as an example. When parsing a Blast file it is also possible to identify the type of ID
Author:
Scooter Willis, Jacek Grzebyta
